item.tloz.demon_fossil.description: Fossil of an ancient demon. Sounds rare, but it turns up all over the place.
item.tloz.stalfos_skull.description: This artifact’s eerie aura makes it the ultimate collector’s item.
item.tloz.star_fragment.description: A sparkly stone that fell from the sky. It’s said to be a piece of a star.
item.tloz.bee_larvae.description: Readily found in beehives. These energizing larvae sell for quite a bit.
item.tloz.wood_heart.description: Whether this acorn is a treasure is debatable, but it does have its fans.
item.tloz.dark_pearl_loop.description: Rare dark pearls, strung together into a stunning necklace.
item.tloz.pearl_necklace.description: Pure white pearls, strung together into a luminous necklace.
item.tloz.ruto_crown.description: Some say this regal crown was worn by generations of Zora princesses.
item.tloz.dragon_scale.description: It’s said that this scale came from a dragon, but no one really knows its origin.
item.tloz.pirate_necklace.description: Once worn by a pirate captain who raided the seas. It has an evil aura.
item.tloz.palace_dish.description: Priceless dish used by past royalty for eating dessert.
item.tloz.goron_amber.description: This tasty Goron treat is valuable because it contains a bug!
item.tloz.mystic_jade.description: Captivating and very valuable because of its beautiful form and color.
item.tloz.ancient_gold_piece.description: This ancient artifact makes you feel like you’ve stepped back in time.
item.tloz.alchemy_stone.description: Desired by many, this artifact is said to bring riches to its owner.
item.tloz.regal_ring.description: A princely ring handed down by royalty for generations.
block.tloz.locked_door.locked_message: You need a key to open this door!
